# Module: `packages/element`

- Element types are immutable — never mutate, always return new objects
- Use `mutateElement()` for controlled mutations inside the package
- Do not add rendering logic here — rendering belongs in `packages/excalidraw`

## How to verify

- `grep -r "\.x =\|\.y =\|\.width =\|\.height =" packages/element/` — direct mutations should not appear outside `mutateElement`
- `grep -r "renderScene\|canvas\|ctx\." packages/element/` — should return nothing
- `yarn test:app packages/element` — run element-specific tests
